scenes.description: Opening intro and transition with red curtains closing and opening to reveal the stage.
Vestia Zeta stands on stage, thanking the audience and sharing her thoughts on the 3D show's theme and production.
Credits roll over a montage of scenes from the show while jazz music plays.
Final end card with a handwritten message from Zeta and background jazz music.
